d him.\n\nAs Lu Xiaolu finds his way, a startling portrait of an economically expanding China comes into view; the propaganda of a common goal gives way to a bottom-line system that he sees as indifferent to individual happiness. But thanks to the relationships he develops, Lu Xiaolu decides to fight for the life he wants.","tmdb_id":222490,"cast":["Hầu Minh Hạo","Yang Caiyu","Hướng Hàm Chi","Phí Khải Minh","Zhang Teng","Chen Yige","Tùy Viên","Trương Tụng Văn","Zhao Qian","Zhang Lei","Wang Yuzheng","Du Rongyi"],"director":["Lin Yu-Hsien"],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"222490","season":1,"vote_average":8,"vote_count":1},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Hầu Minh Hạo","name_vi":"Hầu Minh Hạo","name_original":"Hou Minghao","tmdb_id":1844511,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cKFIKmHNPtAdeaWozo3MZkirojC.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1844511"},{"name":"Yang Caiyu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yang Caiyu","tmdb_id":1276628,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hNIZhvljBtkk19jIxX6nBIwux4K.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1276628"},{"name":"Hướng Hàm Chi","name_vi":"Hướng Hàm Chi","name_original":"Xiang Hanzhi","tmdb_id":2581662,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t4JiiGHKGBBysBUeAaImuZkkUX4.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2581662"},{"name":"Phí Khải Minh","name_vi":"Phí Khải Minh","name_original":"Fei Qiming","tmdb_id":2633279,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iOK3rNtt0bUrDOw5bYoohE3rfiA.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2633279"},{"name":"Zhang Teng","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhang Teng","tmdb_id":4513344,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5aKVrtDry23lILxkFW0xnuRl4tO.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4513344"},{"name":"Chen Yige","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Chen Yige","tmdb_id":4670178,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uwDi5RdBIOPRwaHv6l12Tdv3Zh7.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4670178"},{"name":"Tùy Viên",